	// BLIZZARD    0x27EA2814
	// 
	// 
	// 
	// 
	// 
	// /* OLD INVALID INFO BELOW */
	// Not tested. Based purely on disassembly. Instantly sets the weather to sourceWeather, then transitions to targetWeather over the specified transitionTime in seconds.
