	// In b944, there are 50 (0 - 49) mod types.
	// 
	// Sets the vehicle mod.
	// The vehicle must have a mod kit first.
	// 
	// Any out of range ModIndex is stock.
	// 
	// #Mod Type
	// Spoilers - 0
	// Front Bumper - 1
	// Rear Bumper - 2
	// Side Skirt - 3
	// Exhaust - 4
	// Frame - 5
	// Grille - 6
	// Hood - 7
	// Fender - 8
	// Right Fender - 9
	// Roof - 10
	// Engine - 11
	// Brakes - 12
	// Transmission - 13
	// Horns - 14 (modIndex from 0 to 51)
	// Suspension - 15
	// Armor - 16
